data.description: Owner's pride shows throughout this 3 bd/2.5 bath home located in the quiet neighborhood of St. Georges Hundred! The kitchen boasts upgraded cabinetry with soft close doors/drawers, stunning quartzite counters w/ full backsplash, newly added quartzite eat-in bar, & stainless steel appliances. The family room is light filled & the brick surround & custom made mantel add character to a cozy fireplace. Open the french doors & head out to sip coffee on the screened porch. Finished Bonus Room could make a great hobby room or office! Upstairs, the primary suite has a walk-in closet & beautifully updated bathroom.  Entertain or play in the large, flat, fenced, backyard. Other features include leaf guards, a 8000 watt generator switch & chamberlain quiet smart home garage door opener. Jog only 1/2 mile to the Capital Bike Trail trailhead! Optional/No HOA! Subject to ratified contract with a kick out clause, owner wishes to continue to show property and may accept back up offers.
